manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: PLAN A HEALTHY FUTURE: Since 1984, it has been our mission to provide vitamins and supplements that consistently deliver real health solutions for our customers. Futurebiotics goal is to create a healthy sustainable future through proper supplementation delivered to you and your loved ones.

USDA Organic Vitamin D3 Deficiency in vitamins can easily happen to anyone. As Vitamin D is naturally formed in the body directly from sunshine exposure, its levels can be easily disrupted if our outdoor time is limited. Futurebiotics Certified Organic Vitamin D3 provides the same form of Vitamin D that we obtain from the sun and helps to enable valuable daily replenishment to support immune function, bone health, and strong muscles.*

STANDARDS OF THE FUTURE Futurebiotics formulas are in-house and third party laboratory tested for purity and potency. We only use superior sourced Certified Organic Vitamin D3 that is carefully manufactured at our cGMP Certified Facility that is located in New York. Each and every Futurebiotics product is put through a rigorous process to ensure the integrity of every final product.

RESEARCH & DEVELOPMENT Top-quality research and development is performed by our team of professionals. All of our innovative formulas are held to strict superior standards. LABORATORY TESTED On-site and third party laboratory testing by trained professionals ensure product purity and potency. GMP REGISTERED FACILITY Our GMP (Good Manufacturing Practice) registered facility ensures quality standards and product safety that complies with current regulations. HIGH QUALITY INGREDIENTS We strive to seek out the purest and highest quality ingredients sourced from around the world.

reviews.reviewText: Great value for the money. As advertised

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Good small pills and easy to swallow. I like that it is an high dose of vitamin D and it is a reasonable price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good vitamin to add in the winter.
reviews.reviewText: If you live in a place where you can't get out in the sunshine every day this might be good to add to your diet. I mostly use this supplement in the winter.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: 10,000 IU is a LOT. Usually with these kinds of products you wanna take one a day, but in this case I suggest you do one every two days. With that said it is still a great product for a good price. Remember to take your D especially in winter

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is the second time that I have ordered this product. As far as Vitamin D is concerned, it works well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are chewable, easy to take and not a bad taste. Will buy these again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very high dosage
reviews.reviewText: Had health issues due to low d levels. Needed to increase my d amout. Didn't want to take a lot of pills. These provide a large dosage in one pill at a very good value. Please note, vitamin d is not water soluble, and one can overdose, so you need to check your levels on a regular basis if taking such a high dose.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This has my vitamin D levels up to where they should be. One bottle is a year supply. They're not too big or hard to swallow. You really can't beat the price and most people are deficient in vitamin D.
